      "instruction": "<p><strong>Preheat</strong> the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle </p>\r\n<p><strong>Combine</strong> 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(400ml)</span> of boiled water with the vegetable stock cubes and whisk to combine </p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the veggie mince to the stock and leave to soak until step 5</p>",
