    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cut</strong> the broccoli into small florets</p>\r\n<p><strong>Place</strong> the florets on one oven tray and the gnocchi on a separate oven tray, drizzle both trays with 1-2 tbsp of olive oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> to your taste with salt and pepper and put them in the oven until the broccoli is crisp and the gnocchi cooked (approx. 20 min)</p>",
