      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a wide-based pan with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(3 tbsp)</span> of olive oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>When</strong> hot, add the red onion with a pinch of salt and cook on a medium-low heat for 8-10 min or until softened and starting to caramelise</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> caramelised, add the garlic and cook for a further min, stirring constantly</p>",
